{"tid":1176652,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個細個覺得老豆老母好型嘅時候","createTime":"2019-05-29T10:59:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T11:04:41.000Z","uid":246269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2591fb0c944699f9684c667373933e189a1ee559","tid":1176652,"uid":246269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T10:59:55.000Z","msg":"細個喺樓下同其他人玩鋤大D <br />\n輸咗幾十蚊（事後諗返佢地好似係夾埋呃我錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）         我同佢地話上去攞錢但其實我冇錢俾 勁淆<br />\n上咗去就冇落過去<br />\n第日班人撳門鐘嗌我俾錢<br />\n我問老豆點算 佢攞咗個電話話<br />\n你地係唔係想要錢 上嚟我門口就即刻俾你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班人即刻淆底走佬<br />\n事後老豆冇話我仲同我講唔好同人賭錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然第日落樓俾班人追著嚟屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b61398e3e5e3a6ddddc9a33c80ac36bcfe1dc1d","tid":1176652,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T11:01:24.000Z","msg":"老豆老母捉曱甴 踩死曱甴嗰陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79707c7b4e4b29925755a90fe02c9420b0f02b73","tid":1176652,"uid":181581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T11:04:23.000Z","msg":"佢哋交配嗰陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e2fb1cdd0e96ab4a6ef99d8e76458c26404d66","tid":1176652,"uid":29070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T11:04:41.000Z","msg":"喺我面前扑嘢"}]}